":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/a9/d3/7106_mH6qK.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/a9/d3/7106_mH6qK.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/a9/d3/7106_mH6qK.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/a9/d3/7106_mH6qK.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/a9/d3/7106_mH6qK.jpg"},"summary":"本作故事描述在一个魔术理论与科学共同繁荣进步的世界中，因魔导技术而达繁荣极点的大都市ArkhamCity正面临着恐怖的犯罪组织「Black Lodge」的强大威胁。由身为绝世无双大魔术师的最凶最恶魔人Master Terion所领导的「Black Lodge」，正准备依照自己的欲望进行各种破坏与混乱，并透过最深邃的魔术之力召唤出最强的魔导机器人「鬼械神」。而为了对抗「Black Lodge」的野心，ArkhamCity的守护者「霸道财阀」制作了一款预备与之对抗，并结合了各种魔术理论的精华而成的最强机器人「Demonbane」。但由于「Demonbane」的激活上还欠缺一本力之魔导书，因此「霸道财阀」统帅「霸道琉璃」委托一名三流侦探大十字九郎进行魔导书的搜索工作。而就在大十字进行魔导书搜索工作时，在他面前却出现一名被「Black Lodge」所追缉，身为最强魔导书「Al Azif」的精灵化身少女，并因而与在街道地下沉睡的「Demonbane」相遇，开始故事精彩的波澜变化。 ","name":"機神咆吼デモンベイン","name_cn":"机神咆吼Demonbane","tags":[{"name":"机神咆哮","count":57,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAL改","count":54,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":52,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萝卜","count":39,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中二","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机战","count":35,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2006","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"demonbane","count":32,"total_cont":0},{"name":"坑爹","count":23,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2006年","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2006年4月","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"斩魔大圣","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ED","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补番","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黑田洋介","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"GAL","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Nitro+","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Viewworks","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"増尾昭一","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ヴューワークス","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黒田洋介","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"robo","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"穷","